Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla ‚Äî a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever ‚Äî this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

snippet.description:

For Contact umerhafeez2022@gmail.com 

Topics to be covered in the live stream üëáüèªüëáüèªüëáüèª

India vs South Africa Live Match Today
india vs South Africa Live
India vs South Africa 1st ODI Live
IND vs SA Live Match Today
IND vs SA Live
Live Cricket Match Today 
Cricket Live

When: Sunday, November 30 at 1:30 PM IST

Where: JSCA International Stadium Complex, Ranchi

What to expect: Clear skies are expected for the game. Ranchi's most recent ODI was three years ago and it was South Africa again who had played here in that fixture. The venue usually doesn't witness high-scoring games.

Head-to-head: South Africa lead 51-40 but in India, the hosts lead 18-14

Team News

India

Yashasvi Jaiswal has been patiently waiting for this opportunity to add to his solitary ODI cap. He is expected to open alongside Rohit but India have calls to make in the middle order. Rahul has confirmed that he would bat at six so an allrounder could slot in at five if India seek a sixth option with the ball.

Probable XI: Rohit Sharma, Yashasvi Jaiswal, Virat Kohli, Rishabh Pant (WK), Nitish Reddy, KL Rahul (C), Ravindra Jadeja, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Arshdeep Singh

South Africa

Quinton de Kock's successful comeback to 50-over cricket and Aiden Markram's return should keep Ryan Rickelton out for now. Matthew Breetzke will have to shoulder a lot of responsibility in the middle order after making a spectacular start to his ODI career.

Probable XI: Aiden Markram, Quinton de Kock (WK), Temba Bavuma (C), Matthew Breetzke, Rubin Hermann, Dewald Brevis, Marco Jansen, Corbin Bosch, Keshav Maharaj, Nandre Burger, Lungi Ngidi

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

Here is the teams list that will participate in the next T20 World Cup 2026.

T20 World Cup 2026 teams and groups
Group A: India, Pakistan, Netherlands, Namibia, USA.
Group B: Sri Lanka, Australia, Zimbabwe, Ireland, Oman.
Group C: England, West Indies, Bangladesh, Nepal. Italy.
Group D: South Africa, New Zealand, Afghanistan, UAE, Canada. India vs Pakistan T20 Cricket World Cup Match Will be played on February 15 2026.

snippet.title: Kehna Hi Kya (Lyrical Video) Chitra | A. R. Rahman | Arvind Swamy, Manisha Koirala | Mehboob|Bombay
snippet.description:
#Revibe invites you to immerse yourself in the timeless classic "#KehnaHiKya" by the mellifluous #Chitra, featured in the iconic movie "#Bombay." This musical gem is a journey into the heart of melody and emotion, a song that transcends the boundaries of time and language, leaving an indelible mark on the soul.

Chitra's enchanting vocals in "Kehna Hi Kya" effortlessly convey the depths of love and longing, creating a musical experience that resonates with every listener. With its poetic lyrics and evocative composition, this song has become an anthem of romance and a testament to the power of music to touch the heart.

Credits: 
Singer: Chitra
Music: A. R. Rahman
Lyrics: Mehboob
Movie: Bombay
Starring: Arvind Swamy, Manisha Koirala
Director: Mani Ratnam
Producer: S.Sriram
Label: Universal Music India

snippet.title: Escaping Prison on the Unstable SMP
snippet.description:
i have to escape before i am executed

Escaping Prison on the Unstable SMP / Escaping LAW: Minecraft's Largest Empire

minor spoilers below

featuring: @Spokeishere @PrinceZam @Fantst @Baablu  @loppezz @LettuceK @Lomedy 

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!) (actually I don't think I used any AZALI in this video LOL)
https://www.youtube.com/@andreaszoeller (aria math remix)
https://www.youtube.com/@DMDOKURO (i believe the track that i used is just called void) 

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

Enderal Soundtrack (HQ): Bone Hunter - Knochenj√§ger https://youtu.be/LchGhXSXxZk by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Enderal Soundtrack - Extended (HQ): Run of Things - Lauf der Dinge https://youtu.be/V5mExzEKWs8 by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

 Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Song Lyrics 
meree kismat me too nahee shaayad, kyon teraa intjaar karata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo
aaj samajee hoo pyaar ko shaayad, aaj mai tujhako pyaar karatee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

sochata hoo ke meree aankho ne, kyon sajaaye the pyaar ke sapne
tujhase maangee thee ek khushee maine, tune gham bhee nahee diye apane
jindagee bojh ban gayee abb toh, abb toh jita hoo aur naa marata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo

abb naa tute yeh pyaar ke rishte, abb yeh rishte sanbhaalane honge
meree raaho se tujhako kal kee tarah, dukh ke kaante nikaalane honge
mil naa jaye khushee ke raste me, gam kee parchhayeeyo se daratee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

dil nahee ikhtiyaar me mere, jaan jaayegee pyaar me tere
tujhase milane kee aas hain aa jaa, meree duniya uadas hain aa jaa
pyaar shaayad isiko kahate hai, har ghadee bekaraar rahata hoo
raat din teree yaad aatee hai, raat din intjaar karatee hoo
